In [[Australian Aboriginal mythology]], '''Yalungur''' is a great bird, an [[eagle]] or [[hawk]]. He was [[castrate]]d either by [[Gidja]] or by Gidja's brother [[Mali (mythology)|Mali]] so that Gidja could create the first woman.

